    <innerclass refid="classStmPwm" prot="public">StmPwm</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 PWM wrapper — wraps TIM_HandleTypeDef for <ref refid="classBasePwm" kindref="compound">BasePwm</ref> interface. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Users configure timers + OC channels in STM32CubeMX, then pass the TIM_HandleTypeDef* here. Each <ref refid="classStmPwm" kindref="compound">StmPwm</ref> instance manages one timer with up to 4 channels (CH1–CH4).</para>
